          <span>Node.js</span><span>Express</span><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>Socket.IO</span><span>Railway</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pf-card-links">
          <a href="https://voidsector.up.railway.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="pf-card-btn pf-card-btn--primary">เปิดเว็บ ↗</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/nopparoot15/voidsector_web" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="pf-card-btn">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pf-card pf-card--bot">
        <div class="pf-card-top">
          <div class="pf-card-icon">🤖</div>
          <span class="pf-badge pf-badge--live">Live</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pf-card-name">SaltyBot</h3>
        <p class="pf-card-desc">Discord bot ครบวงจร — Verification, Moderation พร้อม appeal system, Music ผ่าน Lavalink v4, AI (GPT-4.1 + web search) และ Invite tracking</p>
        <div class="pf-card-stack">
          <span>Python</span><span>discord.py</span><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>OpenAI</span><span>Docker</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pf-card-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/nopparoot15/SaltyBot" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="pf-card-btn pf-card-btn--primary">GitHub ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pf-card pf-card--ai">
        <div class="pf-card-top">
          <div class="pf-card-icon">✨</div>
          <span class="pf-badge pf-badge--live">Live</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pf-card-name">ฟ้าใส — Local AI</h3>
        <p class="pf-card-desc">Desktop app แชท AI ภาษาไทย offline 100% รัน LLM ด้วย llama.cpp รองรับ CUDA/ROCm/CPU มีระบบความสัมพันธ์ 5 ระดับ, sprite avatar 8 อารมณ์</p>
        <div class="pf-card-stack">
          <span>Python</span><span>llama-cpp</span><span>Tkinter</span><span>Pillow</span><span>Win32</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pf-card-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/nopparoot15/salty_local_chatbot" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="pf-card-btn pf-card-btn--primary">GitHub ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pf-card pf-card--tts">
